Job Title: Accountants for UAE & Canada
Company: A leading multinational petroleum logistics company with HQ in Dubai
Qualification & Experience: Individuals with exposure in  Oil & Gas industry and able to join immediately will be given preference. Salary will commensurate with experience and skills.
All applicants should have excellent communication skills in English and preferably Hindi / Arabic.
Qualification & Experience: Must be Graduate in Commerce Should have at least 3 – 4 years of experience in preparation of letter of credits, good know how on preparation of cash flows as well as adept in all areas of management accounting. Know how of Oracle or any related financial ERP is mandatory.
Apply: Send their resume to: mailme_job2009@rediffmail.com (OR) Fax to 04-8848003 .
